uww.js
======

Copyright (c) 2026 uww.js contributors

This product is released under the MIT License (see LICENSE).

It contains, in the form of a compiled WebAssembly artifact at
src/_wasm/uww-frontend.{js,wasm} (rebuilt from source in CI, never
committed to this repo), works developed by third parties.

The third-party C sources are fetched at build time from the latest
released sdist of rhasspy/pymicro-features (which itself vendors them
from tensorflow/tflite-micro). The exact upstream version that was
used to compile a given build is recorded inside the package at
`src/_wasm/upstream-version.txt`.

